						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of one <hi rend="italic">achchu</hi> by a <hi rend="italic">kaikkōla</hi> named Māṇikkaṉ Pāṇḍi for a twilight lamp in the temple of Tiruppāṇḍīśvaramuḍaiyār at Āḻvāṉkōyil <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīraśōḻadēvanallūr. The amount was left with the <hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhmaṇas</hi> of the temple.</p>						

						</summary>
